title: Beautifully renovated 3BR + HUGE Den/2BA near Lake of the Isles
posting_body: ['This gorgeous unit has hardwood floors, granite countertops, a kitchen island, dishwasher, central A/C, and stainless steel appliances!', 'It has three large bedrooms PLUS a spacious third floor den and two full bathrooms.', 'The bedrooms are pictured with carpet, but have new hardwood installed that match the hardwood in the hallway picture.', 'Just a block from the Wedge Coop, it is centrally located near Uptown and Downtown Minneapolis surrounded by multiple restaurants, coffee shops, and near Lake of the Isles.', 'Just 6 minutes to Target Corporate HQ, 7 minutes to Allina Health HQ and Abbott Northwestern Hospital, and 4 minutes to the Minneapolis College of Art and Design.', 'Virtual showings available.', 'Masks are required for in-person showings.', 'Utilities: Tenants pays gas, electric, and optional internet.', 'Landlord pays water and trash.', 'Snow removal, lawn care, and maintenance included.', 'Wired for fiber optic internet from USI.', 'Laundry in building.', 'Deposit: $2095', '$400 nonrefundable pet fee.', 'Application fee: $39.99 per applicant.', 'Income: Applicants combined must make 3X rent.', 'Applicants must have verifiable consistent income.', 'Credit:', 'Each applicant must have credit score 650 or higher.', 'Background: Applicants must have a clear background check.', 'Rental history: Applicants will not be approved if they have negative rental history, including but not limited to previous evictions or unlawful detainers.']
